page.title: 20NEWTOWN METHODIST CHURCH
page.content: NEWTOWN METHODIST CHURCH, GT. YARMOUTH, AND CREDITS. We visited the Church, we liked the organ best,it was kept so nice. On it is a cross with a picture of an anchor on it( possibly from a fishermens' church). A diary of the organ is also kept. Mr. Cooper, the present oganist, took over from his father. Material collected by class 4R(age 12):Steven Attenborough,Matthew Clark, Simon Clark,Shaun French,Paul Hoyle, Scott Pawsey,Martin Prime, Stuart Sahota,Ian Starling,Karen Brewer,Tina Kirk,Sarah Cattee,Hannah Burton,Marsha Chapman,Sarah Cooke,Karen Conway,Linda Myhill,Joanne Driver,Tracey Hart,Liza Smith,Corrina Haylett,Rachel Hollis, Ellena Kiki,Angela Littlewood,Verena Palmer,Melanie Carr,Sharon Saunders, Clare Squires. Teachers: Gordon (Jim) Roberts & Gerald Thomas.
